&gt; &lt;a  rel="nofollow" href="https://w3c.github.io/webappsec-secure-contexts/#is-origin-trustworthy"&gt;https://w3c.github.io/webappsec-secure-contexts/#is-origin-trustworthy&lt;/a&gt;,
&gt; clause #5.
