&gt;&gt;&gt; &lt;a  rel="nofollow" href="https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/API/ClipboardItem/ClipboardItem#data"&gt;https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/API/ClipboardItem/ClipboardItem#data&lt;/a&gt;)
