&gt;&gt; libraries out there we can look at? This one
&gt;&gt; &lt;&lt;a  rel="nofollow" href="https://github.com/isocroft/browsengine"&gt;https://github.com/isocroft/browsengine&lt;/a&gt;&gt; does not use it.
