&lt;span class="subject"&gt;&lt;a href="/search?l=blink-dev@chromium.org&amp;q=subject:%22Re%5C%3A+%5C%5Bblink%5C-dev%5C%5D+Intent+to+Ship%5C%3A+Attribution+Reporting+Feature%5C%3A+Remove+ar_debug+Requirement%22&amp;o=newest" rel="nofollow"&gt;&lt;span itemprop="name"&gt;Re: [blink-dev] Intent to Ship: Attribution Reporting Feature: Remove ar_debug Requirement&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
