I realized that we have a usage counter but in a wrong place
&lt;&lt;a  rel="nofollow" href="https://source.chromium.org/chromium/chromium/src/+/main:third_party/blink/renderer/core/timing/performance_navigation_timing.cc;l=429;bpv=1;bpt=1?q=WebFeature::kBackForwardCacheNotRestoredReasons%20-f:out&amp;ss=chromium"&gt;https://source.chromium.org/chromium/chromium/src/+/main:third_party/blink/renderer/core/timing/performance_navigation_timing.cc;l=429;bpv=1;bpt=1?q=WebFeature::kBackForwardCacheNotRestoredReasons%20-f:out&amp;ss=chromium&lt;/a&gt;&gt;,
