&lt;span class="date"&gt;&lt;a href="/search?l=blink-dev@chromium.org&amp;q=date:20241006" rel="nofollow"&gt;Sun, 06 Oct 2024 21:49:20 -0700&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
